# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears in the introductory section of a
# user guide for a scientific simulation application, explaining the basic
# functionality and navigation of the TI Planning Tool interface.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown 2026-06-16T14:42:30Z
#: osparc/product/quickStart/tis/Welcome.js
msgid ""
"        This quick tutorial gives a basic overview of how the TI Planning "
"Tool works and how to navigate through the interface.<br>        We will "
"focus on two main aspects, how to:<br>        - Use the platform<br>        "
"- Get started with a New Plan<br>      "
msgstr ""
"        Este tutorial rápido ofrece una visión general básica de cómo "
"funciona la Herramienta de Planificación TI y cómo navegar por la interfaz."
"<br>        Nos centraremos en dos aspectos principales, cómo:<br>        - "
"Usar la plataforma<br>        - Comenzar con un Nuevo Plan<br>      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears in the user interface of a
# scientific simulation application, specifically on the main screen where
# users manage their simulation plans.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown 2026-06-16T14:42:31Z
#: osparc/product/quickStart/tis/Dashboard.js
msgid ""
"        The Dashboard is your private hub which contains all of your Plans "
"as well as Plans that have been shared with you.         From the Dashboard "
"you are able to open your Plan or create a New Plan from scratch.      "
msgstr ""
"El Panel de Control es tu centro privado que contiene todos tus Planes, así "
"como los Planes que han sido compartidos contigo. Desde el Panel de Control "
"puedes abrir tu Plan o crear un Nuevo Plan desde cero."

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears as an instructional tooltip or guide
# within the user interface of the application, explaining the process of
# creating a new study plan.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown 2026-06-16T14:42:33Z
#: osparc/product/quickStart/tis/Dashboard.js
msgid ""
"        1) New Plan: by clicking on this card a new study will be created "
"and open.        The planning process will be presented in three successive "
"steps that will be described more in detail in the following steps.      "
msgstr ""
"1) Nuevo Plan: al hacer clic en esta tarjeta se creará y abrirá un nuevo "
"estudio. El proceso de planificación se presentará en tres pasos sucesivos "
"que se describirán con más detalle en los siguientes pasos."

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears in the user interface of a
# scientific simulation application, guiding users on how to manage and
# interact with TI Plans within the software.
# CTX-VERSION: unknown 2026-06-16T14:42:35Z
#: osparc/product/quickStart/tis/Dashboard.js
msgid ""
"        2) The other cards are TI Plans that were already created by you or "
"shared with you. You can reopen them to do further analysis         or by "
"clicking three dots, on the top right corner, you can share, delete or "
"check the details and metadata.      "
msgstr ""
"2) Las otras tarjetas son Planes TI que ya fueron creados por ti o "
"compartidos contigo. Puedes reabrirlos para hacer un análisis adicional o, "
"haciendo clic en los tres puntos en la esquina superior derecha, puedes "
"compartir, eliminar o verificar los detalles y metadatos."

