"most advanced tissue models, for directly analyzing biological real-world "
"phenomena and complex technical devices in a validated biological and "
"anatomical environment.        <br>        <br>        In order to "
"facilitate the introduction to the platform, we have some Guided Tours that "
"can be found in the Help & Support section.        <br>        <br>        "
"For more specific technical information, please refer to the Manuals.      "
